Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:11.24,Top - s,,0,0,0,,真岛一伙通过了预想中的起爆点  第一瞭望台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,玉簪  你能回来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:17.33,Top - s,,0,0,0,,他们现在固守在第二瞭望台  切断了电梯电源
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那个… 我有话一直想要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:22.29,Top - s,,0,0,0,,选中的队伍从 4 个应急楼梯突袭第二瞭望台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,玉簪？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫千束来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,请回到你的座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,司令  千束她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她不会来  我和她断了联系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,断了联系？店长也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这和我们无关
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在开会中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种情况下  他们俩都断了联系…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有什么古怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在作战开始前回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你把手机留下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,之后只准用这个通讯方式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,服从我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了  赶紧的  机器小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哦？你认识我？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟现在我可是超越 Walnut 的最强黑客呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,出… 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不接电话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,900,0,,贵宾休息室！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:03.74,Default,,0,900,0,,太爽了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次觉得和你在一起真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,先不提我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道不应该陪千束到最后一刻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我陪她已经够久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,倒是你还这么见外做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,明明已经在 LycoReco 打成一片了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那时真是开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最后一次见你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,头等舱机票  谢谢你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你的是经济舱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,经… 经济…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,停业？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们 30 分钟后重新突袭  快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,千束不在店里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她把手机留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有些古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能是真岛做了什么手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,前几天你对真岛说的「吉松」又是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是千束的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是提供心脏给她的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真岛他知道千束在找吉松
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真岛在延空木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你有什么想知道的  直接去问他本人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在他临死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,最接近千束心脏的是哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,详细调查这个作者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  她肯定用了假名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要用元数据  而是用脸部识别搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在起飞时请不要使用好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,短时间里也起飞不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找地址
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小工坊么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有什么线索
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,长得像是吉松的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  分析振动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,转换成声音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,直接见面不是严令禁止的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. 吉松
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,博士  我找到了个很好的实验对象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,正中靶心！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,用这骨骼数据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,和之后 10 年的数据比对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去年？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,都是多亏了亚伦的援助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是帮了你一把
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,仅以一位少女的生命做代价
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就能让你的才能开花结果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是很划算的买卖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,给她这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需要操心未来成千上万的患者就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,受试者就交给我来处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她和你一样  同是亚伦的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,您失散多年的女儿在那里等您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,女儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:13.32,Top,,0,0,0,,赶快点  山茱萸  快下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认识她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,得赶紧联系温哥华的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还没开始交往嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,千束的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,另外还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.14,Top - s,,0,0,0,,我的肌肉帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是在吉松手上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,亚伦援助的研究者造出了改良版的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,而它就在吉松手上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那边  走这边  山茱萸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不准命令我  小丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,吉松现在在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全找不到他最近几天的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,永别了 Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我之后再联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前去了趟 LycoReco
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  停业了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  那是千束的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只有手机留在店里  千束和店长都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,看样子是发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以分析这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了  稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,黑客？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,万事俱备了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一定可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,第二幕开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这么一条路吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,被选中的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,各自使用 4 个应急楼梯抵达第二瞭望台后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻夺回在真岛控制下的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,东西南北 4 座直通电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在第一瞭望台待机的部队依次乘电梯上升
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,与上面的队伍会合  歼灭敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不要心慈手软  全部杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没法目视确认敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,玉簪  快看千束的手机！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这张图片发到了她手机上  然后她收到了吉松的来电
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在米卡的车在押上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他们两个应该是去旧电视塔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说  千束正在前往持有心脏的人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,玉簪  一切都解决了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我有不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那可能是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,以千束的身手应该不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这肯定有什么不对头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  玉簪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要被其它队伍抢先了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  但我得先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么又来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,玉簪  怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去千束那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你被她传染了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是还在执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,苳  让她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我会替代她的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,归根结底  这家伙会被开除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因为你的过失啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对  都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,当时真的是太对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,欧石楠！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了  我说的都是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是退出这次任务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那就再也没法回到 DA 咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你最后的机会哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里拯救不了千束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么向司令部汇报啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正在征集好点子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好  电梯下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪她  搞得功劳都被其它队伍抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这又不是在比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  真血腥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,启动电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Alpha 队已抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她们就不能帮忙启动了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这果真是比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,来一决高下吧
Comment: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,(石蒜系统,Radiata)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,石蒜系统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.39,RUBY,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(960,980)}Radiata
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊  我又来打扰你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,诶  又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么又被劫持了？
Comment: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,(石蒜,Radiata)无法应对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,石蒜无法应对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.40,RUBY,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(835,980)}Radiata
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,从外部…  不  那也不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,系统受到大量攻击  已经把全部资源放在生成防火墙上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,铁壁般的防御反倒是害了你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好好领教一下我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,都内的大约 100 个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有好好享受你们的第一把枪  和第一份自由吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说  在享受之前  就有这样的家伙们来妨碍你们？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要千万注意穿这种制服的小丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  那是…
Comment: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她们是国家的秘密特工  (彼岸花,Lycoris)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她们是国家的秘密特工  彼岸花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:27.53,RUBY,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1285,980)}Lycoris
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为了维持日本的和平神话  她们不择一切手段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事都做得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,光看视频也难以让人信服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟视频造假可容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们应该也有在大街上看到她们吧？
Comment: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亲眼看到真正的(彼岸花,Lycoris)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亲眼看到真正的彼岸花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:13.54,RUBY,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1177,980)}Lycoris
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,让她们千万不要开枪！
Comment: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,(石蒜系统,Radiata)怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,石蒜系统怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.04,RUBY,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(804,980)}Radiata
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,重启需要一些时间  要重启吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,全国每年有 3000 人失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是 3000 人啊
Comment: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,其中有多少是被(彼岸花,Lycoris)抹去的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,其中有多少是被彼岸花抹去的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:32.26,RUBY,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1022,980)}Lycoris
Comment: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你们这些看见了(彼岸花,Lycoris)的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你们这些看见了彼岸花的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:35.23,RUBY,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1146,980)}Lycoris
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只要自己生活幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那就不在乎这个不自然和不平衡世界了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是想从自诩为神的人手中夺回自然的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这段视频也会被他们抹去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们要记住自己亲眼所见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是真相  也是打倒这些家伙的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,总部  请指示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,防御！
Comment: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,与延空木中的(彼岸花,Lycoris)失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,与延空木中的彼岸花失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:25.57,RUBY,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1022,980)}Lycoris
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,干！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的要一个人去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,您回店里去喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那替我向真司问好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,保重！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,干！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那台很贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好  第三幕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  各位  快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,从楼梯上摔下去一不留心就会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就用…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  好险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好险！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好哦  做得不错  再坚持一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,又是这里么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,吉叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我是千束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,千束！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,吉叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊  大英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真岛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,吉叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要是躲开  你最宝贵的吉叔就会中弹咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你问我为什么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这是延空木传来的直播画面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,武装起来的少女正不断开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,苳
Comment: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的(彼岸花,Lycoris)正在全国出道中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的彼岸花正在全国出道中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:47.87,RUBY,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(835,980)}Lycoris
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这下你们就玩儿完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你能看到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我能听到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,能靠细微动作判断对方射击的方向和时机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这能力真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪亚伦会感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,声音么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,视觉就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以吗？那可是实弹的哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我从吉叔那听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你因为无聊的限制荒废了自己的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但我就喜欢你的这点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我也讨厌强迫人使用某种方式生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要把我和你相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不如我们联手打倒亚伦机关吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是严刑拷问  吉叔也是什么都不招
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你和我说不定可以联手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不都说了我找的不是你吗？
